(a) Notwithstanding another law to the contrary, the bridge on State Route 242
(Buffalo Road) spanning Crawfish Creek near the intersection of such route with
Flatwoods Road in Lawrence County, is hereby designated the "Johnny R. Thompson
Memorial Bridge" to honor the memory of this respected, lifelong resident of Lawrence
County who was known for his integrity, strong work ethic, devotion to family, and
commitment to his community.
(b) The department of transportation is directed to erect suitable signs or to affix
suitable markers designating the bridge described in subsection (a) as the "Johnny R.
